settings.heading: Paper Type
settings.content:
These are kiss cut stickers that are not waterproof/ fadeproof.

✱ REGULAR MATTE sticker paper - 80gsm, less saturated print, matte paper finish, best for bujos and planner, writable (not waterproof)

✱ VINYL MATTE (not laminated)- high quality print, long lasting and smudge proof. (Not weatherproof and scratch proof)

Carefully peel off the stickers to avoid tearing it.

settings.heading: Please read me!
settings.content: NOTE: This is a handmade sticker I designed and produced at home with my home inkjet printer and Silhouette cutter. While I try to make sure that everything is cute and in perfect condition, they are still prone to small imperfections. I hope you understand. ♥️
